{
  "stem": "27507.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I had to go to the main streets sometimes because my mother's family lived in Leszno, which was one that I went quite often to see them.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were living in Leszno, I think 71.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I can check it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that was one of the main streets, of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you saw beggars everywhere, as I said, and dressed in rags.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then the rags were getting worse and worse and torn and sometimes barefoot and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then they were dying as well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The beggars were dying, and the poor people were dying, generally, and the poorer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And if somebody died, if the family had no means of burying him, they would just take him out of the house and put him in the street.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lying covered with newspapers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the street.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the street next to the wall of the house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Those were, of course, the poorest who were-- who were dying and being buried in the street.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were more people who were buried not in such a-- who were dying not in such an obvious fashion, who were dying maybe in their flats and taken out of there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there were-- but the Chevra Kadhisha, the burial service, was working all the time, and they were going with carts through the ghetto and collecting those--",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--dead bodies who were lying at the side of the street.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you saw them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One-- one saw them in the main street, although I didn't look.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You saw just something lying there covered with a newspaper.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But sometimes I saw-- sometimes I remember I went somewhere and went in the small ghetto and then went back.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
